<html>
<h1>How to Play Part 1: Starting a new game.</h1>
<p>When open the game, you will be greeted with a window. That looks like this:</p>
<img src="res/0.png"/>
<p>Or like this on Mac.</p>
<img src="res/1.png"/>
<p>You probably have already gone there if you can open this.</p>
<p>Then, click on 'Start game'.</p>
<p>You will be greeted with a window that looks like this:</p>
<img src="res/2.png"/>
<p>These are the options you can have for your universe generation.</p>
<p>You can play around with them later, but for now, click 'Done'</p>
<p>Wait for a few moments for the universe to generate, and there you go, your universe has been generated.</p>
<br/>
<p>Here are what the different options do.</p>
<table>
    <tr>
        <th>Option</th>
        <th>Description</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <th>Universe Size</th>
        <th>Determines the size of the galaxy you are creating</th>
    </tr>
</table>
</html>